name: UAnimCurveCompressionCodec_ACL
doc: Uses the open source Animation Compression Library with default settings suitable for general purpose animation curves.

CurvePrecision: The curve precision to target when compressing the animation curves.
MorphTargetPositionPrecision: The mesh deformation precision to target when compressing morph target animation curves.
MorphTargetSource: The skeletal mesh used to estimate the morph target deformation during compression.
